data.description:
Discover the allure of this exquisite Victorian home in Leavenworth! Boasting 5 bedrooms and 3.5 baths, its spacious interior is filled with character and modern updates. From the charming sitting room to the expansive kitchen with ample storage and an island, every room exudes a perfect blend of charm and functionality. The tall ceilings enhance the elegance of the office and living rooms, while the enormous laundry/mud room provides practicality. Outside, a large porch invites you to unwind. Make this your dream home – come explore its unique charm today!

New Roof, new A/C unit!
